---
// Sektion 8: Split-CTA mit Magnetic Buttons (SM-05)
---

<section class="split-cta">
  <div class="split-cta__side split-cta__side--dark">
    <div class="split-cta__inner">
      <span class="split-cta__caption">Du überlegst noch</span>
      <h3 class="split-cta__title">Sprich mit<br/><em>Torsten & Lothar.</em></h3>
      <p class="split-cta__body">30 Minuten am Telefon. Kein Verkaufsdruck, keine Folie. Nur ehrliche Fragen und Antworten zu Verbund, Wechsel und Konditionen.</p>
      <a href="/makler-werden#kontakt" class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" data-magnetic data-cursor-label="Erstgespräch">
        Erstgespräch anfragen
        <svg width="18" height="14" viewBox="0 0 18 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 7h15M12 1l5 6-5 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="split-cta__side split-cta__side--light">
    <div class="split-cta__inner">
      <span class="split-cta__caption">Du bist schon entschieden</span>
      <h3 class="split-cta__title">Direkt<br/><em>Partner werden.</em></h3>
      <p class="split-cta__body">Formular ausfüllen, wir melden uns zeitnah mit dem Anbindungs-Fahrplan. Einfacher geht's nicht.</p>
      <a href="/makler-werden#formular" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-magnetic data-cursor-label="Jetzt registrieren">
        Zur Registrierung
        <svg width="18" height="14" viewBox="0 0 18 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 7h15M12 1l5 6-5 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .split-cta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 72vh;
  }
  .split-cta__side {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: clamp(3rem, 8vh, 6rem) var(--padding-x);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .split-cta__side--dark {
    background: var(--color-primary-darker);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .split-cta__side--light {
    background: var(--color-bg-warm);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .split-cta__side::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(184,134,91,0.12), transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .split-cta__side--light::before {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(10,25,64,0.06), transparent 50%);
  }

  .split-cta__inner {
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .split-cta__caption {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .split-cta__side--light .split-cta__caption { color: var(--color-accent-dark); }

  .split-cta__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 0;
    color: inherit;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 75;
  }
  .split-cta__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .split-cta__side--light .split-cta__title em { color: var(--color-accent-dark); }

  .split-cta__body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 46ch;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .split-cta__inner .btn {
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .split-cta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .split-cta__side { padding-block: 4rem; }
  }
</style>
